            (shapes
              (circle 0 0 8 '#xA9DFBF)))
    (entity 'lane4
            (placement (* t 140) 400)
            (shapes
              (circle 0 0 8 '#x7DCEA0)))))
```

[VISUAL: Four horizontal lanes, each with a circle moving left-to-right at increasing speeds from top to bottom. The top lane is slowest, the bottom lane fastest.]

A visual **velocity gradient**: slower at top, faster at bottom.

