### Spirals: Radial and Angular Motion Combined

An entity spiraling outward with constant angular and radial velocities:

```scheme
(define (route t)
  (let* ((cx 240)
         (cy 240)
         (r (* t 50))
         (theta (* t 3.0))
         (x (+ cx (* r (cos theta))))
         (y (+ cy (* r (sin theta)))))
