              (placement x y)
              (shapes
                (circle 0 0 5 '#xF39C12))))))
```

[VISUAL: An orange dot spiraling outward from the center in a smooth expanding helix.]

Radial velocity: 50 px/s. Angular velocity: 3.0 rad/s. The combination produces a spiral.

