### Zero Velocity

An entity at rest—zero velocity, fixed position:

```scheme
(define (route t)
  (world
    (entity 'stationary
            (placement 240 240)
            (shapes
              (circle 0 0 20 '#x95A5A6)))))
```

[VISUAL: A gray circle sitting motionless at the center of the canvas.]

Velocity = 0. Position constant for all t. The baseline against which all motion is measured.

